{"id": "art-9434", "label": "Art. 9434", "title": "Art. 9434: Soluţionarea cererii", "slug": "art-9434", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1450630051\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1048\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1450630051\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 943<sup>4</sup>:\nSolu&#355;ionarea cererii </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_841784545\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1047\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_841784545\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Cererea se solu&#355;ioneaz&#259; în camera de consiliu,\ncu citarea în termen scurt a mandantului sau, dup&#259; caz, a beneficiarului\ncontractului de mandat de ocrotire &#351;i a mandatarului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1054271395\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1046\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1054271395\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Solu&#355;ionarea cererii se face cu participarea\nprocurorului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_967271729\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1045\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_967271729\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Instan&#355;a este obligat&#259; s&#259; îl asculte pe\nmandant sau, dup&#259; caz, pe beneficiarul contractului de mandat, punându-i\n&#351;i întreb&#259;ri pentru a constata necesitatea &#351;i oportunitatea\nîncuviin&#355;&#259;rii mandatului de ocrotire. Dispozi&#355;iile art. 940\nalin. (3) teza final&#259; &#351;i alin. (4) sunt aplicabile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_757047696\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1044\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_757047696\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Instan&#355;a verific&#259; dac&#259; mandantul a\ndesemnat prin contract o persoan&#259; c&#259;reia mandatarul trebuie s&#259;\nîi dea socoteal&#259;, iar, în caz contrar, desemneaz&#259; o asemenea\npersoan&#259;, cu acordul acesteia.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_440207433\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1043\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_440207433\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Dispozi&#355;iile art. 940 alin. (7) r&#259;mân\naplicabile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1736808016\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1042\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1736808016\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Dac&#259; sunt îndeplinite condi&#355;iile\nprev&#259;zute de lege, instan&#355;a încuviin&#355;eaz&#259; mandatul de\nocrotire prin încheiere.</span></p>"}